OL,3,CUp to 6,800 new inpatient beds may be
OL,4,Cneeded by 2040, report finds
OL,6,FPublic acute hospitals will need to
OL,7,Fincrease inpatient bed capacity by
OL,8,Fbetween 40% and 60% by 2040, according
OL,9,Fto a new report.
OL,11,FA continued increase in population,
OL,12,Fparticularly at older ages, will drive
OL,13,Fthe increased demand, according to the
OL,14,FEconomic and Social Research Institute
OL,15,Fpublication on Wednesday.
OL,17,FIreland's population is projected to
OL,18,Fincrease from 5.3 million in 2023 to
OL,19,Fbetween 5.9-6.3 million by 2040, with
OL,20,Fthe range reflecting differing
OL,21,Fassumptions on future migration trends.
