OL,3,CUp to 6,800 new inpatient beds may be
OL,4,Cneeded by 2040, report finds
OL,6,FThe number of people aged 65 years and
OL,7,Fover will increase from 1 in 7 of the
OL,8,Fpopulation in 2023 to 1 in 5 by 2040.
OL,10,FThis age group are particularly high
OL,11,Fusers of hospital services, accounting
OL,12,Ffor over 60% of inpatient bed days in
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FThe Department of Health-funded
OL,16,Fresearch projects that emergency
OL,17,Fdepartment attendances will grow from
OL,18,F1.6 million to more than two million
OL,19,Fby 2040.
