OL,3,CUp to 6,800 new inpatient beds may be
OL,4,Cneeded by 2040, report finds
OL,6,FOutpatient department attendances are
OL,7,Fprojected to grow from 4.6 million in
OL,8,F2023, to between 5.5 and 5.9 million
OL,9,Fby 2040.
OL,11,FDay patient discharges are projected
OL,12,Fto grow from 1.2 million in 2023, to
OL,13,Fbetween 1.5 and 1.6 million.
OL,15,FInpatient discharges are projected to
OL,16,Fgrow from 650,000 to up to 900,000.
OL,18,FInpatient bed days are projected to
OL,19,Fincrease from 3.9 million in 2023, to
OL,20,Fbetween 5.1 and 6.0 million in 2040.
