OL,3,CUp to 6,800 new inpatient beds may be
OL,4,Cneeded by 2040, report finds
OL,6,FThe ESRI research states that there
OL,7,Fwill be a requirements for an
OL,8,Fadditional 650 to 950 day patient beds
OL,9,Fby 2040 ` a growth of between 25-37%.
OL,11,FIn addition, it projects a requirement
OL,12,Ffor between 4,400 to 6,800 inpatient
OL,13,Fbeds ` an increase of between 40% and
OL,14,F60%.
OL,16,FEven at the lower end of the
OL,17,Fprojections, the report highlights the
OL,18,Fneed for substantial additional
OL,19,Fcapacity to meet increases in demand
OL,20,Ffor hospital services by 2040.
