OL,3,CUp to 6,800 new inpatient beds may be
OL,4,Cneeded by 2040, report finds
OL,6,FThe analysis shows how different
OL,7,Fpolicy choices like reducing inpatient
OL,8,Flength of stay and waiting list
OL,9,Fmanagement can alter the projections.
OL,11,FDr Aoife Brick, senior research
OL,12,Fofficer at the ESRI and lead author of
OL,13,Fthe report, said: "Our findings
OL,14,Fhighlight significant future growth in
OL,15,Fdemand for public acute hospital
OL,16,Fservices, driven primarily by
OL,17,Fpopulation growth and ageing. The
OL,18,Freport offers policymakers evidence on
OL,19,Fthe scale of service expansion needed
OL,20,Fto meet future demand."
