OL,3,CUp to 6,800 new inpatient beds may be
OL,4,Cneeded by 2040, report finds
OL,6,FMinister for Health, Jennifer Carroll
OL,7,FMacNeill welcomed the review and said:
OL,8,F"This evidence base is crucial for
OL,9,Ffuture planning, ensuring we have the
OL,10,Ffacilities to provide the best care to
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,F"Increasing bed numbers and the
OL,14,Fnecessary resources and workforce
OL,15,Frequires careful long-term planning."
OL,17,FThe Programme for Government has
OL,18,Fcommitted to delivering thousands more
OL,19,Fbeds through the acute bed capacity
OL,20,Fexpansion plan, new surgical hubs and
OL,21,Felective treatment centres.
